snippet.textDisplay:
Dear Abony, 

Whenever I listen this song, I think of you. Over the last few months, I have been trying to forget you and removing every memories with you but It's hard a lot. The more i try to forget you, the more i remember you. You will never understand what i feel inside and it’s like burning myself.

I am carrying all memories in my heart that's why i can not move on.


Life is unpredictable and short and it’s truly painful living without you but i pray for you and my prayers and thoughts are with you.

I miss you and now missing you and will miss you forever.


Always be happy wherever you are now in this world.

Regards,
Hedonist
